etism of carbon-based materials. Lastly the peculiarities of the magnetic\nbehavior of some related materials and the trends for future developments were\nmentioned.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Mar 2013 08:52:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-03-26"}
